    ⚡ HOW THE PROGRAM WORKS:
    ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
    
    🔹 CORE TECHNOLOGY
    Poker All-In Calculator operates through a sophisticated Monte Carlo simulation engine that runs millions of hand combinations per second. The software analyzes your hole cards, community cards, and estimated opponent ranges to calculate precise winning probabilities. It uses advanced statistical algorithms to account for hand combinations, blockers, and dead cards, providing accurate equity calculations for pre-flop, flop, turn, and river scenarios. The calculator supports Texas Hold'em, Omaha, and other popular poker variants .
    
